column5: For those that fish in the province of Quebec, take note that there is 800 new lakes on the Navionics data base so if you ask yourself about renewal of you're subcription you got the answer! There is also 40 lakes that has been update by the community. You can view those new lakes on the chart viewer:https://webapp.navionics.com/?lang=e...c%7BxdHnv%7CcM
